duties_responsibilities.duty: Design and develop solutions, serving as Technical Lead for projects to support Business needs.
Serve as a technical mentor for junior developers, providing guidance and ensuring coding standards are followed.
Successfully deliver technical solutions to business problems using system development life cycle methodology development processes, practices, and artifacts.
Comprehend design specifications and understand the business functions performed by the assigned business unit.

education_certification.credential: Bachelor’s degree in business or computer science (Master's preferred)
